BGTASK


provides an object with a worker thread interface and implementation of start(), stop(), status(), join().
Derived objects are instatiated in stopped state.
 
overridable functions are onwakeup

---------------------------------------------------------------
566334bb4831b867551c4e10f61efb7623fbda48
void c::wakeup()
    calls reset_resume() setting the internal state to resume
    calls onwakeup() so specializations can signal their sleeping thread.   


